1
00:00:02,736 --> 00:00:03,869
I get it.

2
00:00:03,870 --> 00:00:05,171
We need to build chemistry.

3
00:00:05,638 --> 00:00:06,678
But is it really necessary

4
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,141
to share a bed?

5
00:00:09,376 --> 00:00:10,509
I'll just sleep on the couch.

6
00:00:10,510 --> 00:00:11,510
No...

7
00:00:12,245 --> 00:00:14,180
How can you let a
bed get the best of you?

8
00:00:14,581 --> 00:00:16,783
I'm the one who'll look
unprofessional on screen.

9
00:00:18,218 --> 00:00:19,219
Which side do you want?

10
00:00:19,586 --> 00:00:20,586
Either is fine.

11
00:00:21,221 --> 00:00:22,221
Yes.

12
00:00:24,691 --> 00:00:25,859
No shower, no bed.

13
00:00:26,092 --> 00:00:27,092
Why?

14
00:00:28,094 --> 00:00:28,795
Come on.

15
00:00:28,796 --> 00:00:30,963
But I'm exhausted.

16
00:00:30,964 --> 00:00:33,566
I'll just shower in the morning.

17
00:00:35,277 --> 00:00:39,137
[More fans leaving insufferable
comments about the pairing]

18
00:00:43,076 --> 00:00:44,144
What are you looking at?

19
00:00:44,644 --> 00:00:46,579
Nothing. Just checking some notes.

20
00:00:49,215 --> 00:00:50,483
Did you find the mission card?

21
00:00:51,251 --> 00:00:52,385
Oh, right. I totally forgot.

22
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:55,088
Mission two is sleeping together.

23
00:00:55,488 --> 00:00:56,923
I wonder what mission three is.

24
00:00:57,323 --> 00:00:58,792
They said it's on the bed.

25
00:00:59,926 --> 00:01:01,327
On the bed?

26
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:18,511
We're being filmed.

27
00:01:18,845 --> 00:01:19,813
For an idol,

28
00:01:19,814 --> 00:01:21,213
is this really okay?

29
00:01:21,214 --> 00:01:22,314
This is just how I am.

30
00:01:22,315 --> 00:01:23,715
I'm like this once I'm comfortable.

31
00:01:24,484 --> 00:01:25,484
Right...

32
00:01:25,685 --> 00:01:26,719
I need to give this back.

33
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,188
Can you help me out?

34
00:01:35,328 --> 00:01:37,597
These two necklaces look great.

35
00:01:38,465 --> 00:01:39,399
But...

36
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:41,100
one's double rings, one's a single wing.

37
00:01:42,702 --> 00:01:43,770
You're quite

38
00:01:44,204 --> 00:01:46,206
a walking contradiction.
